data.description: Priced for a Quick Sale! Professional photos coming soon!  Brand New Modern Farmhouse on 21+ rolling acres of pastoral landscape. An absolutely stunning setting! Conveniently located in growing Monroe County just minutes from the interstate with close proximity to Knoxville, Maryville, the Smoky Mountains and Chattanooga.  Meticulously designed with all of the latest luxury upgrades...no detail left undone. A few of the highlighted amenities include: a state-of-the-art kitchen with commercial appliances, custom cabinetry, hidden walk-in pantry, quartz countertops with lifetime warranty, 9' ceilings throughout, hidden room for 'safe storage', Alexa enabled lighting, spray in insulation on the entire home, energy efficient DC fans, dual laundry rooms-one on each level, abundant storage space, encapsulated crawl space, underground electric, public water PLUS a deep well for outside water use; plumbed and wired for a pool, 6' gutters with underground drainage, front and back covered porches and so much more.  Sellers will provide an allowance at closing with an acceptable offer for driveway, landscaping, closet and pantry shelving.  This will enable the buyers to add their finishing touches and make it their own. The perfect multi-generational property with first right of refusal on an adjoining 5 acres with a home. Plenty of wide open space for expansion or for growing families to experience what peaceful, country living is all about!
